{"tid":370742,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實打風公司有冇權扣人工/大假?","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T10:42:20.000Z","uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72a7cc72b1e8e5ef7d88bddde78abaeb45160d66","tid":370742,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1258247ab8478d161b9826b81d084276c73058f4","tid":370742,"uid":102091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"好似冇，毒果新聞講過"},{"pid":"b9119561ef13d3b32e2009127b2ec0c6b25127c0","tid":370742,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"緊係唔得啦 <br />\n告到佢含家產"},{"pid":"65ab9e5c5f0c45ab018e00cd2b4b0a5fc1f0135b","tid":370742,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"聽講新加坡先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a9897be438652037a215b36a663464df88387b","tid":370742,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"工資的扣除<br />\n颱風和暴雨都是自然災害，即使事先未有訂明工作安排，但僱員由於惡劣<br />\n天氣或因不受控制的因素影響而缺勤，僱主不應扣除他們的工資。同樣，<br />\n他們的勤工獎也不應受到影響。<br />\n對於那些須按訂明的工作安排上班但缺勤或遲到的僱員，僱主不應不問情<br />\n由地扣除他們的工資，而須了解原因，並考慮每宗個案的獨特情況。<br />\n<br />\n年假、法定假日及休息日<br />\n如僱主減少僱員有權享有的年假、法定假日及休息日，以補償因發出八號<br />\n或以上颱風警告或黑色暴雨警告而損失的工作時間，即屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n《颱風及暴雨警告下的工作守則》－勞工處"},{"pid":"2c2564a40763cf32bed709bc2af4e51d0b85c198","tid":370742,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:20:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07f79af286c35471374c6e228f0900514dcdd46a","tid":370742,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:21:43.000Z","msg":"話就話冇，實際上係有<br />\n<br />\n你告囉，唔想撈啊？"},{"pid":"2fe0bbd91a1bcab7b12ddd511500e1c0bf21f7b1","tid":370742,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話就話冇，實際上係有<br />\n<br />\n你告囉，唔想撈啊？</blockquote><br />\n告，首先你無左份工<br />\n然後你發現自己無錢同公司打官司，亦無收入維生，又可以套用我最鐘意既一句『法律面前，窮人含撚』"},{"pid":"69bbb2b41b456a4060202639d8107bb2466c3100","tid":370742,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話就話冇，實際上係有<br />\n<br />\n你告囉，唔想撈啊？</blockquote><br />\n告，首先你無左份工<br />\n然後你發現自己無錢同公司打官司，亦無收入維生，又可以套用我最鐘意既一句『法律面前，窮人含撚』</blockquote><br />\n唔好再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd812df750a4cc0ee2f3485a529056aad3ecf916","tid":370742,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408fdeac911b0d7be7857eb7fb20b1e86e757747","tid":370742,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"push"}]}